Output docs/assets/hero.gif

Require uv

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1200
Set Height 700
Set Theme "Dracula"
Set TypingSpeed 0ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 0.8

Hide
Type "export PS1='$ '"
Enter
Ctrl+L
Show
Type "uv run --extra dashboard python demo/demo_workflow.py"
Sleep 1.2s
Enter
Sleep 5.2s
